<Body>  	<Title>湖南一造纸厂数千吨芦苇起火 16小时扑灭</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009-7-30</ReportTime>
<Content>
	
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Location lid="l1">益阳市大通湖区金北顺造纸厂芦苇堆场</Location>发生<Denoter did="d1" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>着火部位于该堆场的北角，<Event eid="e2"><Location lid="l2">堆场</Location>内<Denoter did="d2" type="operation">存放</Denoter>有<Object oid="o2">大型芦苇堆垛18个</Object></Event>，共有1.8万多吨的芦苇。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e3"><Denoter did="d3" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter>发生后</Event>，<Event eid="e4">益阳、岳阳、常德3地<Participant sid="s4">消防官兵</Participant>用了<Time tid="t4" type="timeInterval">16个小时</Time>彻底将<Object sid="s4">大火</Object><Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">扑灭</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e5"><Time tid="t5" type="relTime">当晚7时50分</Time>，大通湖区<Participant oid="o5">消防大队</Participant>接到该区<Participant sid="s5,s6">金北顺造纸有限公司</Participant><Denoter did="d5" type="operation">报警</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e6"><Denoter did="d6" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e7"><Location lid="l7">厂区内芦苇堆垛</Location>发生<Denoter did="d7" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
			<Sentence><Event eid="e8"><Denoter did="d8" type="operation">接警</Denoter></Event>后，<Event eid="e9"><Participant sid="s9">大队</Participant>迅速<Denoter did="d9" type="operation">出动</Denoter>2台<Object oid="o9">消防车</Object><Participant oid="o9">6名官兵</Participant></Event><Event eid="e10"><Denoter did="d10" type="movement">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l10">现场</Location></Event>。<Event eid="e11">由于芦苇堆垛上的<Object oid="o11">芦苇</Object>已被<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d11">晒干</Denoter></Event>，<Event polarity="negative" eid="e12"><Object sid="s12">消防水枪</Object>无法对<Location lid="l12">现场</Location><Object oid="o12">火势</Object>进行有效<Denoter did="d12" type="operation">控制</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e13"><Object sid="s13">大火</Object>从<Location lid="l13" type="origin">两个堆垛</Location>迅速<Denoter did="d13" type="movement">蔓延</Denoter>到<Location lid="l13" type="destination">5个堆垛</Location></Event>，且火场火势已处于猛烈燃烧阶段，烟雾很浓。</Sentence><Sentence>幸运的是，火灾现场无易燃易爆等危险源，<Event polarity="negative" eid="e14">无<Participant sid="s14">人员</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d14">被困</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence>经过<Event eid="e15">全体<Participant sid="s15,s17">参战人员</Participant>奋力<Denoter did="d15" type="operation">扑救</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e16"><Time tid="t16" type="timeInterval">到29日凌晨3时</Time>，<Object oid="o16">火势</Object>得到有效<Denoter did="d16" type="operation">控制</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e17"><Time tid="t17" type="relTime">上午10时</Time>，<Object oid="o17">大火</Object>基本被<Denoter did="d17" type="stateChange">扑灭</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>根据现场情况，为防止死灰复燃，<Event eid="e18"><Participant sid="s18">消防人员</Participant>迅速开展<Denoter type="operation" did="d18">余火清理</Denoter>工作</Event>，<Event eid="e19"><Time tid="t19" type="timeInterval">到中午12时</Time>，在2台挖掘机的配合下，<Object oid="o19">余火</Object>被彻底<Denoter did="d19" type="stateChange">扑灭</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e20">周边堆垛1万多吨价值近千万元的<Object oid="o20">芦苇</Object>被<Denoter type="operation" did="d20">保住</Denoter>了</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e21">经<Participant sid="s21">消防部门</Participant>初步<Denoter did="d21" type="operation">查明</Denoter></Event>，这起<Event eid="e22"><Denoter did="d22" type="emergency">火灾</Denoter></Event>系<Event eid="e23">该厂<Object sid="s23,24">员工</Object>在<Denoter did="d23" type="movement">转运</Denoter><Object oid="o23">芦苇</Object></Event>时<Event eid="e24"><Denoter did="d24" type="operation">违规操作</Denoter></Event>所致。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e25"><Time type="relTime" tid="t25">目前</Time>，<Participant oid="o25">2名违规操作的工人</Participant>已被<Participant sid="s25">警方</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d25">控制</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		
